==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Lavasan'''

# Lavasan is a city near Tehran, in [[Iran]]. Lavasan refers to two cities: "Lavasan-e-Bozorg" and "Lavasan-e-Kochak". Lavasan is a "touristy" and beautiful city. It is known as "beverly hills of iran", where you can find the most beautiful multimillion dollar villas of Iran, there. The most expensive neighborhood of Lavasan is [[Astalak]].